lead_paragraph: Former world number one Caroline Wozniacki, one point from falling behind 5-0 in the opening set, rallied to upset ninth-seeded Russian Svetlana Kuznetsova in straight sets at the U.S. Open on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Wozniacki Rallies to Upset Ninth Seed Kuznetsova
headline.main: Wozniacki Rallies to Upset Ninth Seed Kuznetsova
